52WkHigh.description: Highest price traded in the last year

52WkLow.description: Lowest price traded in the last year

askSize.description: Quantity of shares in block currently requested for trade

bidSize.description: Quantity of shares in block currently offered for trade

closePrice.description: Price of last executed trade in last completed session

cusip.description: A nine-character alphanumeric code that identifies a North American financial security for the purposes of facilitating clearing and settlement of trades

delayed.description: True if price quote is not real time

description.description: Name for the security being quoted

digits.description: Number of decimal places used for bid and ask prices

divAmount.description: Unadjusted U.S. dollar amount of latest annual cash dividend

divDate.description: Payment date of latest cash dividend

exchange.description: Primary marketplace for trading of this security, expressed as a single-letter abbreviation

exchangeName.description: Upper case abbreviation of primary exchange for trading of this security

highPrice.description: Maximum execution amount in last completed session

lastPrice.description: Final execution amount in current session

lastSize.description: Quantity of shares in block most recently traded

lowPrice.description: Minimum execution amount in last completed session

marginable.description: True if security can be used for trading by means of borrowing a certain percentage of its value

mark.description: Current share value calculated based on market bid, market ask, and last traded price

markChangeInDouble.description: Change in calculated share price from last full session

markPercentChangeInDouble.description: Change in calculated share price from last full session, expressed as a proportion

nAV.description: Value per share calculated for certain securities based on assets held

netChange.description: Difference in share price from last full session

netPercentChangeInDouble.description: Difference in share price from last full session, expressed as a proportion

openPrice.description: Initial trade price during trading session for which the quote is diplayed

peRatio.description: A valuation measure for a compay calculated as the propotion of current share price to earnings

quoteTimeInLong.description: Epoch milliseconds when current data was generated

realtimeEntitled.description: True if pricing for the security can be generated without delay

regularMarketLastPrice.description: Final quote generated during standard trading hours

regularMarketLastSize.description: Number of shares last traded as a block during standard trading hours

regularMarketNetChange.description: Difference in share price since the end of the last session of standard trading hours

regularMarketPercentChangeInDouble.description: Difference in share price since the end of the last session of standard trading hours, expressed as a proportion

regularMarketTradeTimeInLong.description: Epoch milliseconds when the last buy/sell transaction occurred for the security during standard trading hours

shortable.description: True if security can be borrowed for sale to be repurchased later

symbol.description: String of characters used to identify an equity

tradeTimeInLong.description: Epoch milliseconds when the last buy/sell transaction occurred for the security

totalVolume.description: Number of shares traded in the quoted trading session

volatility.description: A measure of the price range in which a security has been trading
